Upgrading from version 2.8.23 to 2.8.24

1. install SQL-Ledger over top
   # cd /usr/local
   # tar zxvf sql-ledger-2.8.24.tar.gz

2. fix permissions
   # chown -hR nobody:nogroup *
   # chmod 711 templates users css spool

Note: replace nobody:nogroup with your web server user and group

3. copy
   
   Default-reminder1.html
   Default-reminder2.html
   Default-reminder3.html
   Default-reminder1.tex
   Default-reminder2.tex
   Default-reminder3.tex
  
   without the "Default-" prefix to the user's template directory

4. log in

